{"article_id":"sulD5aY71o4c9dk5","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The Justice Department has filed criminal charges against several suspects in the Benghazi terror attack ,","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"a U.S. official tells .","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"The U.S. official confirmed","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"that sealed charges were filed against suspects in connection with the Sept. 11 , 2012 , attack .","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"It 's unclear whether they are the same individuals","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"whose images the FBI released to the public in May .","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"One of the individuals","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"charged","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"is Libyan militia leader Ahmed Khattalah .","depth":4},{"id":9,"text":"In an interview","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"conducted last October ,","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"Khattalah told","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"that he was at the scene of the attack that night .","depth":4},{"id":13,"text":"He also expressed no remorse for the death of Ambassador Chris Stevens ,","depth":4},{"id":14,"text":"who was killed in the attack on the U.S. compound along with three other Americans .","depth":4},{"id":15,"text":"Daily politics news delivered to your inbox :","depth":3},{"id":16,"text":"sign up for our newsletter","depth":3},{"id":17,"text":"But in the extended interview , Khattalah denied to","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"that he was a `` ringleader '' of the attack ,","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"as he has been identified by others .","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"He also said","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"he was not a member of the militant group Ansar al-Shariah ,","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"said to be involved .","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"Khattalah also denied to at the time","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"that he was `` on the run . ''","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"He said","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"no U.S. officials had made an effort","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"to contact him or detain him .","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"It has been alleged that Khattalah helped direct the attack .","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"He told","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"that he was just `` directing traffic '' outside of the compound","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"that had become congested with vehicles .","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"While denying being a member of the militant group ,","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"he expressed admiration for its goals","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"and said","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"he was in contact with various members of that and other militias","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"active in Benghazi .","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"The administration was staying mum on reports of the Benghazi charges .","depth":5},{"id":38,"text":"Asked about the reports ,","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"a Justice Department official said only","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"that their investigation is `` ongoing . ''","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"`` It has been ,","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"and remains ,","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"a top priority .","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"We have no further comment at this time , ''","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"the official said .","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"The development comes","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"just days after Republican members of Congress put new pressure on the incoming FBI director , James Comey , to renew focus on the investigation .","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"`` It has been more than 10 months since the attacks .","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"We appear to be no closer to knowing","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"who was responsible today","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"than we were in the early weeks","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"following the attack .","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"This is simply unacceptable , ''","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"they wrote in a letter to Comey last week .","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"House Oversight and Government Reform Committee Chairman Darrell Issa , R-Calif. ,","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"who last week issued two new subpoenas to the State Department for documents on Benghazi ,","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"says","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"it is imperative the suspects be placed in U.S. custody and questioned as soon as possible ,","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"if the DOJ has indeed identified them .","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"\" Usama Bin Laden had been criminally charged long before the September 11 , 2001 , terrorist attacks","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"but was not apprehended , ''","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"Issa said in a statement .","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"`` Delays","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"in apprehending the suspected Benghazi killers","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"will only put American lives at further and needless risk . \"","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"The Sept. 11 attack","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"-- led by militants","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"who used heavy weapons","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"including rocket-propelled grenades and mortars --","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"took place in two phases .","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"The first was an assault on the U.S. consulate .","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"The second wave targeted the nearby CIA annex ,","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"where U.S. personnel had gone","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"to take cover .","depth":10}],"relations":[{"parent":149,"left":89,"right":148,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":89,"left":83,"right":88,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":83,"left":80,"right":82,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":80,"left":76,"right":79,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":76,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":79,"left":77,"right":78,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":77,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":78,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":82,"left":81,"right":8,"